{"tid":591551,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"［認真一問］消化食物要四個鐘？","createTime":"2018-03-13T15:40:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-14T07:37:00.000Z","uid":172823,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"eb938477e06815c3923b43b30bde81023f8ecbbc","tid":591551,"uid":172823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T15:40:29.000Z","msg":"細個聽啲長輩講晚飯要早少少食，如果唔係喺訓教個陣會頂住個胃，其實真唔真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n食野又話咩要四個鐘先消化，咁我食粒糖係咪都要四個鐘先消化完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇ching可以解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8408e9d98ae73cc88b9b0499af39aa14cfc00ac4","tid":591551,"uid":172823,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T15:41:07.000Z","msg":"例如食一粒呢個<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/13/234104_2a390900b0817d1563b7e7b3fbc9cecc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F13%2F234104_2a390900b0817d1563b7e7b3fbc9cecc.png&h=506bdc64&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bf623e0a8f597c7e4187159ef4c923d79f13da2f","tid":591551,"uid":62494,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T15:41:36.000Z","msg":"係,好似我呢D腸胃唔好既要仲耐少少先消化完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a25ddfaee0d2c459e7e495d9a5b7ea450f630135","tid":591551,"uid":127251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T15:43:36.000Z","msg":"糖應該未吞都可以溶晒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2163dd6a7eac565167ebbdf7b70c686f02d3bd1a","tid":591551,"uid":172823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf623e0a8f597c7e4187159ef4c923d79f13da2f","tid":591551,"uid":62494,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T15